cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CR, cs.NE 

The paper deals with the generation of adversarial examples using GANs, which is a popular topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of adversarial examples to attack classifiers is also relevant to the fields of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and cryptography (cs.CR). Finally, the use of GANs to generate adversarial examples is related to the field of neural networks (cs.NE).
